{"tid":2226133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大國會取消每年支那國慶升旗儀式","createTime":"2020-10-01T21:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T01:24:56.000Z","uid":284729,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3888701346f95929add45ef72f9106301a2e7b35","tid":2226133,"uid":284729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T21:07:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rcinet.ca/en/2020/09/30/ontario-legislatures-plans-to-fly-chinese-flag-in-ceremony-are-scotched/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rcinet.ca%2Fen%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2Fontario-legislatures-plans-to-fly-chinese-flag-in-ceremony-are-scotched%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdApE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=7351579a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rcinet.ca/en/2020/09/30/ontario-legislatures-plans-to-fly-chinese-flag-in-ceremony-are-scotched/</a><br />\n近年加拿大國會每年10月1日都會升支那國旗 今年於公眾壓力下取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBowing to pressure, skepticism and criticism, the Ontario government has backed off on a controversial flag-raising ceremony honouring China at the province&rsquo;s legislature that was to take place shortly after noon today.<br />\n<br />\nThe legislature was set to commemorate China&rsquo;s National Day, Oct. 1, which marks the founding of the republic by the Chinese Communist Party in 1949.<br />\n<br />\nChina&rsquo;s consul-general in Toronto, Han Tao, was set to speak at the event and politicians and diplomats of all stripes were due to attend.<br />\n<br />\nApparently overlooked by organizers were the two Canadians&ndash;former diplomat Michael Kovrig and businessman Michael Spavor&ndash;who are currently in prison in China on what most believe are trumped up charges.<br />\n<br />\nThe backlash and criticism mounted quickly. <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I don&rsquo;t think any order of government in Canada should be flying the flag of the People&rsquo;s Republic of China while two Canadian citizens are wrongfully imprisoned in China,&rdquo; the federal Conservative Party&rsquo;s foreign affairs critic, Michael Chong, said Tuesday.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;When governments fly a foreign flag it sends a certain signal.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nBoth the NDP and Liberals said Tuesday they would not be sending any of their provincial legislators to the event.<br />\n<br />\nTheir boycott followed a similar one at Toronto City Hall on by Mayor John Tory on Monday. <br />\n<br />\nLate Tuesday, the sergeant-at-arms at the Ontario Legislature, Jackie Gordon, announced that <span class=\"red\">the event and all future flag-raisings were being cancelled because of COVID-19.</span>"},{"pid":"d322832fdb85d2fc84ba81b071013f8ad578837b","tid":2226133,"uid":284729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T21:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dd00bc1fbd2586c6a9e0b33b6371df992c1901","tid":2226133,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T21:19:07.000Z","msg":"安大略省議會<br />\n唔係渥太華嘅國會"},{"pid":"84fd9f311a416a75100149cb3cfb15b408183b80","tid":2226133,"uid":270889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T21:46:35.000Z","msg":"because of 武肺 <br />\nnot CCP atrocities"},{"pid":"4c40659bf09f9da578e5c7a7f768808efb84e369","tid":2226133,"uid":279326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:00:14.000Z","msg":"支那大獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4296c203c0a0f5287128d048d7cb52201ef7d02","tid":2226133,"uid":289486,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84fd9f311a416a75100149cb3cfb15b408183b80","tid":2226133,"uid":270889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T21:46:35.000Z","msg":"because of 武肺 <br />\nnot CCP atrocities"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:42:12.000Z","msg":"係因為中國捉左兩個加拿大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13834deda9fb533cff06ea253eca152ef7d0131","tid":2226133,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ced6bac821f486293e51c6d903a204bc599038f","tid":2226133,"uid":75072,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T00:14:18.000Z","msg":"支拿大真係好撚癲 幫其他國國昇旗"},{"pid":"4e8527786b30af20d0bebadc636de7bee8e0d090","tid":2226133,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T00:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ca923d7e8b608d8a119cb68fa7555260fb7bf0","tid":2226133,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T00:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c68eb426652376f1aad0358532cb023dcf210e2","tid":2226133,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T00:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cf684525dd79c8232b9c52efce388b92ff978d","tid":2226133,"uid":128261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T00:58:49.000Z","msg":"撐港Michael Chong係混血兒，老豆係香港移民，老母係白人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10